snippet.title: Chocolate Chip Cookie Mix In A Jar
snippet.description: A gift of love from your own kitchen.

snippet.title: Chocolate Dipped Cranberry Cookies
snippet.description: Enjoy the rich flavors in these Chocolate Dipped Cranberry Cookies. Perfect for snacks and great for entertaining, too.

snippet.title: Frozen Chocolate-Covered Cappuccino Crunch Cake
snippet.description: Cappuccino Crunch Cake combines coffee ice cream, pound cake and NESTLÉ® TOLL HOUSE® Milk Chocolate Morsels for a rich and creamy frozen dessert! This dessert was created by Beth Royals of Richmond, VA.

snippet.title: Chocolate Pate with Cranberry Coulis
snippet.description: Chocolate Pate with Cranberry Coulis is a terrific choice when you are looking for a dessert that is delicious, beautiful and different.

snippet.title: Poached Pears with Chocolate Cranberry Sauce
snippet.description: Poached Pears with Chocolate Cranberry Sauce is an elegant dessert.

snippet.title: Chocolate Yummies
snippet.description: Chocolate Yummies are a great blend of semi-sweet morsels and cereal. This delicious dessert is quick and easy and perfect for all occasions.

snippet.title: Chocolate Truffles
snippet.description: Your holiday party will become special when you serve this delicious Chocolate Truffle.

snippet.title: Chocolate Rhapsody
snippet.description: Inspire romance any day of the week with this recipe for indulgence. With its divine raspberry mousse and moist yellow sponge cake separated by a thin layer of decadent chocolate, Chocolate Rhapsody is sure to make love abound.

snippet.title: Layers Of Love Chocolate Brownies
snippet.description: A finalist in the 2000 Share The Very Best Recipe Contest, this recipe was entered by Alma Carey of Sarasota, FL. Made with a genuine love of chocolate, this decadent brownie features vanilla-flavored white and semi-sweet chocolate morsels, chopped pecans and caramel layered within a rich cocoa batter.

snippet.title: Original NESTLÉ® TOLL HOUSE® Chocolate Chip Cookies
snippet.description: This famous classic American cookie is a treat no matter what the age or occasion. Enjoy it with a glass of cold milk.
